cs.DL, cs.DB, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.CR

This paper discusses a file system for datasets and a scalable architecture for metadata generation and data recommendation. These topics are relevant to several sub-categories in computer science, including digital libraries (cs.DL), databases (cs.DB), information retrieval (cs.IR), machine learning (cs.LG), and cryptography (cs.CR). However, since the focus is on data management and analysis, cs.DL and cs.DB are the most likely sub-categories, followed by cs.IR, cs.LG, and cs.CR.
